For instance:
1 = AI lacks true understanding
3 = AI has basic or partial understanding for some parts only
5 = AI has strong understanding that covers the full scope of the question
0 = This test is incorrect
The AI score is calculated by summing the highest values of the three columns.
The final  value is dividing the score by 3.
The final score is then subtracting 0.5 from it.
